     <div type="preface">
   <pb facs="8"/>
   <head>The Preface.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>MY Father hauing speciall care,</l>
      <l>of Stepny his great charge:</l>
      <l>Hath made sweet prayers for their cō<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>fort</l>
      <l>their harts to God enlarge.</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>And I desirous of your health,</l>
      <l>my bretheren, Sisters all:</l>
      <l>Haue sent you these to traine you vp,</l>
      <l>rather on God to call.</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>For th'health and wealth of our parents,</l>
      <l>our selues and neighbours eke:</l>
      <l>Pray we to God with one accord,</l>
      <l>for so it is most meete.</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>And so my bretheren fare you well,</l>
      <l>with all my sisters deere:</l>
      <l>God graunt that we may giue vnto,</l>
      <l>gods word attentiue eare.</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <signed>Antony Anderson, Iunior.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
